s|Russian Championships]]'''||bgcolor=gold|1st||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd||4th||10th||bgcolor=silver|2nd||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd\n|-\n| width=\"50\" rowspan=\"1\" |'''2014'''||align=left|'''[[Russian Rhythmic Gymnastics National Championships|Russian Championships]]'''||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd||||bgcolor=gold|1st||bgcolor=silver|2nd||6th||bgcolor=silver|2nd\n|-\n| width=\"50\" rowspan=\"1\" |'''2013'''||align=left|'''[[Russian Rhythmic Gymnastics National Championships|Russian Junior Championships]]'''||bgcolor=silver|2nd||||||||||\n|-\n| width=\"50\" rowspan=\"1\" |'''2012'''||align=left|'''[[Russian Rhythmic Gymnastics National Championships|Russian Junior Championships]]'''||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd||||||||||\n|-\n| width=\"50\" rowspan=\"1\" |'''2011'''||align=left|'''[[Russian Rhythmic Gymnastics National Championships|Russian Junior Championships]]'''||8th||||||||||\n|-\n! align=center colspan=8  |  ''Q = Qualifications (Did not advance to Event Final due to the 2 gymnast per country rule, only Top 8 highest score);'' <br /> ''WD = Withdrew;''  ''NT = No Team Competition''\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em|refs=\n<ref name=figws14>{{cite web | url = http://www.fig-gymnastics.com/site/files/page/editor/files/2014%20RG%20WR%20Archives.pdf | title = FIG World standings for rhythmic gymnastics | publisher = International Federation of Gymnastics| accessdate = 14 April 2014 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=figws15>{{cite web | url = http://www.fig-gymnastics.com/site/files/page/editor/files/2015%20RG%20WR%20Archives.pdf | title = FIG World standings for rhythmic gymnastics | publisher = International Federation of Gymnastics| accessdate = 14 April 2015 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=figws16>{{cite web | url = http://www.fig-gymnastics.com/site/files/page/editor/files/2016%20RG%20WR%20Archives.pdf | title = FIG World standings for rhythmic gymnastics | publisher = International Federation of Gymnastics| accessdate = 14 April 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=figws17>{{cite web | url = http://www.fig-gymnastics.com/site/page/view?id=262 | title = FIG World standings for rhythmic gymnastics | publisher = International Federation of Gymnastics| accessdate = 30 August 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Tashkent2016>{{cite web|title=Yana Kudryavtseva completes fifth career World Cup sweep in Tashkent|url=http://www.fig-gymnastics.com/site/figNews/view?id=1555 |publisher=International Federation of Gymnastics |date=17 May 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=WCMinsk16>{{cite web | url = http://www.fig-gymnastics.com/site/figNews/view?id=1561 | title = Margarita Mamun sweeps in Minsk; Belarus defeats Russia in Rhythmic Group competition | publisher = International Federation of Gymnastics| accessdate = 24 May 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=WCKazan16>{{cite web | url = http://www.fig-gymnastics.com/site/figNews/view?id=1604| title = Margarita Mamun defeats Yana Kudryavtseva in Kazan | publisher = International Federation of Gymnastics| accessdate = 12 July 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=RusNat17>{{cite web|url=http://www.allsportinfo.ru/index.php?id=109012 |title= \u0414\u0438\u043d\u0430 \u0410\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0438\u043d\u0430 \u2013 \u0447\u0435\u043c\u043f\u0438\u043e\u043d\u043a\u0430 \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u0438 \u043f\u043e \u0445\u0443\u0434\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u0433\u0438\u043c\u043d\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0435 \u0432 \u043c\u043d\u043e\u0433\u043e\u0431\u043e\u0440\u044c\u0435|accessdate=2017-03-12}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Euros17>{{cite web | url = http://www.gymmedia.com/Rhythmic-Gymnastics/2017-Europeans-Rhythmic-Gymnastics | title = 2017 Europeans of Rhythmic Gymnastics | publisher = Gymmedia |date=21 May 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Injury17>{{cite web | url = http://tass.ru/sport/4479371 | title = \u0412\u0438\u043d\u0435\u0440: \u0421\u043e\u043b\u0434\u0430\u0442\u043e\u0432\u0430 \u043d\u0435 \u0443\u0441\u043f\u0435\u043b\u0430 \u0432\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0442\u044c\u0441\u044f \u043f\u043e\u0441\u043b\u0435 \u0442\u0440\u0430\u0432\u043c\u044b \u043a \u0427\u041c \u043f\u043e \u0445\u0443\u0434\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u0433\u0438\u043c\u043d\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0435 | publisher = Itar-Tass |date=13 August 2017}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n\n* {{FIG|id=20096|name=Aleksandra Soldatova}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20140325112527/http://www.rhythmicgymnasticsresults.com/ Rhythmic Gymnastics Results]\n* {{Instagram|soldy21_}} Instagram\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Soldatova, Alexandra}}\n[[Category:1998 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Sterlitamak]]\n[[Category:Russian rhythmic gymnasts]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the Rhythmic Gymnastics World Championships]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Russian rhythmic gymnast}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2014}}\n{{Infobox gymnast\n|name= Aleksandra Soldatova\n|image= Soldatova2.jpg\n|imagesize= 280px\n|caption= Soldatova at the [[2014 Rhythmic Gymnastics World Cup Series|2014 Debrecen World Cup]]\n|fullname= Aleksandra Sergeyevna Soldatova\n|altname= Alexandra Soldatova\n|nickname= Sasha, Sanchos, Soldy and Sashulka\n|country={{RUS}}\n|formercountry=\n|birth_date= {{birth date and age|df=yes|1998|06|01}}\n|birth_place=[[Sterlitamak]], [[Bashkortostan]], Russia\n|hometown= [[Pushkino, Moscow Oblast]]\n|residence= [[Dmitrov]], Moscow Oblast\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height= 174 cm \n|weight= 55 kg \n|discipline=RG\n|level= senior\n|natlteam= 2012\u2013present\n|club= Gazprom \n|gym= Novogorsk\n|collegeteam=\n|headcoach= [[Irina Viner]]\n|assistcoach= [[Anna Shumilova]]\n|formercoach=\n|choreographer= Lyudmila Dimitrova, Tatiiana Pomerantseva\n|music=\n|eponymousskills= \n|retired= \n|show-medals=yes\n|worldranking= '''2''' ''[[2019 FIG Rhythmic Gymnastics World Cup series|WC]]''<ref>{{cite web |url=\nhttps://www.fig-gymnastics.com/site/rankings/ranking_rg.php |title=Rhythmic Gymnastics World Ranking 2019 Individ