ic Gymnastics European Championships|European Championships]]'''||||bgcolor=gold|1st||7th||||8th||\n|-\n|align=left|'''[[2015 FIG Rhythmic Gymnastics World Cup Series|World Cup Pesaro]]'''||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd||||8th (Q)||bgcolor=gold|1st||3rd (Q)||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd\n|-\n|align=left|'''[[2015 FIG Rhythmic Gymnastics World Cup Series|World Cup Bucharest]]'''||6th||||20th (Q)||4th (Q)||bgcolor=silver|2nd||bgcolor=gold|1st\n|-\n|align=left| '''[[2015 FIG Rhythmic Gymnastics World Cup Series|World Cup Lisbon]]'''||bgcolor=gold|1st||||6th||bgcolor=silver|2nd||bgcolor=gold|1st||4th (Q)\n|-\n|align=left| '''[[Rhythmic Gymnastics Grand Prix Series|Grand Prix Moscow]]'''||4th||||13th (Q)||bgcolor=gold|1st||7th||4th (Q)\n|-\n| width=\"50\" rowspan=\"9\" |'''2014'''||align=left| '''Italian Serie A'''||||bgcolor=gold|1st||||||||\n|-\n|align=left| '''[[2014 World Rhythmic Gymnastics Championships|World Championships]]'''||||bgcolor=gold|1st||4th (Q)||4th (Q)||||\n|-\n|align=left|'''IV International Brazil Meet'''||bgcolor=gold|1st||||bgcolor=gold|1st||bgcolor=gold|1st||bgcolor=gold|1st||bgcolor=gold|1st\n|-\n|align=left|'''Izmir Tournament Cup'''||bgcolor=gold|1st||||bgcolor=silver|2nd||bgcolor=silver|2nd||bgcolor=silver|2nd||bgcolor=gold|1st\n|-\n|align=left|'''[[2014 Rhythmic Gymnastics World Cup Series|Tashkent World Cup]]'''||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd||||4th (Q)||4th (Q)||3rd (Q)||3rd (Q)\n|-\n|align=left|'''[[2014 Rhythmic Gymnastics World Cup Series|Corbeil-Essonnes World Cup]]'''||4th||||4th (Q)||bgcolor=silver|2nd||12th (Q)||3rd (Q)\n|-\n|align=left|'''Baltic Hoop'''||bgcolor=gold|1st||||bgcolor=gold|1st||4th||bgcolor=gold|1st||bgcolor=gold|1st\n|-\n|align=left|'''[[2014 Rhythmic Gymnastics World Cup Series|Debrecen World Cup]]'''||bgcolor=gold|1st||||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd||bgcolor=silver|2nd||bgcolor=gold|1st||bgcolor=gold|1st\n|-\n|align=left|'''[[Rhythmic Gymnastics Grand Prix Series|Gazprom International Tournament]]'''||bgcolor=CC9966|3rd||||||||||\n|-\n!align=center colspan=