k/news/2019/may/saddlers-to-visit-notts-county-in-pre-season/ |publisher=[[Walsall F.C.]] |accessdate=6 July 2019}}</ref> [[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Aston Villa to visit the Banks's in pre-season |url=https://www.saddlers.co.uk/news/2019/june/aston-villa-to-visit-the-bankss-in-pre-season/ |publisher=[[Walsall F.C.]] |accessdate=6 July 2019}}</ref> and [[Tranmere Rovers F.C.|Tranmere Rovers]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Tranmere friendly confirmed |url=https://www.saddlers.co.uk/news/2019/may/tranmere-friendly-confirmed/ |publisher=[[Walsall F.C.]] |accessdate=6 July 2019}}</ref>\n\n{{football box collapsible\n|date = {{Start date|2019|07|06|df=y}}\n|time = 15:00 [[British Summer Time|BST]]\n|round = [[Exhibition_game#Association_football|Friendly]]\n|score = 2\u20131\n|report = https://www.saddlers.co.uk/news/2019/july/match-report-for-alfreton-town-vs-walsall-fc-on-06-jul-19/\n|team1 = [[Alfreton Town F.C.|Alfreton Town]]\n|team2 = [[Walsall F.C.|Walsall]]\n|stadium = [[North Street (stadium)|Impact Arena]]\n|location = [[Alfreton]]\n|referee = \n|result = L\n|goals1 = [[Josh Clackstone|Clackstone]] {{goal|39}}<br />[[Morgan Brough|Brough]] {{goal|88}}\n|goals2 = [[Elijah Adebayo|Adebayo]] {{goal|6}}\n|attendance = \n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date = {{Start date|2019|07|09|df=y}}\n|time = 19:45 [[British Summer Time|BST]]\n|round = [[Exhibition_game#Association_football|Friendly]]\n|score = 1\u20131\n|report = https://www.saddlers.co.uk/news/2019/july/match-report-for-leamington-vs-walsall-fc-on-09-jul-19/\n|team1 = [[Leamington F.C.|Leamington]]\n|team2 = [[Walsall F.C.|Walsall]]\n|stadium = Phillips 66 Community Stadium\n|location = [[Leamington Spa]]\n|referee = \n|result = D\n|goals1 = [[Colby Bishop|Bishop]] {{goal|64}}\n|goals2 = Trialist {{goal|76}}\n|attendance = \n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date = {{Start date|2019|07|13|df=y}}\n|time = 15:00 [[British Summer Time|BST]]\n|round = [[Exhibition_game#Association_football|Fr